#: src/gui-gtk4/siril_intro.c:61
msgid ""
"A new menu, Tools, has been created to centralize Siril's tools, which were "
"previously scattered throughout the interface. It now includes statistics, "
"FITS header, astrometry and photometry tools, as well as image analysis "
"features."
